Achievements.Name: First Hurdle
Achievements.Description: Survive Agent Diagnostics and earn deployment into Pacific City.

Achievements.Name: Get Connected
Achievements.Description: Locate and activate an Absorption Unit, alone or with another Agent.

Achievements.Name: Plugged In
Achievements.Description: Locate and activate every Absorption Unit in Pacific City, alone or with another Agent.

Achievements.Name: Big Bang
Achievements.Description: Oversee the deployment and successful detonation of a Beacon, alone or with another Agent.

Achievements.Name: Hope Springs Savior
Achievements.Description: Detonate every Beacon in Hope Springs, alone or with another Agent.

Achievements.Name: Green Bay Savior
Achievements.Description: Detonate every Beacon in Green Bay, alone or with another Agent.

Achievements.Name: Unity Heights Savior
Achievements.Description: Detonate every Beacon in Unity Heights, alone or with another Agent.

Achievements.Name: Light Bringer
Achievements.Description: Detonate every Beacon in Pacific City, alone or with another Agent.

Achievements.Name: All Under Control
Achievements.Description: Secure all Tactical Locations within one Cell stronghold, alone or with another Agent.

Achievements.Name: Location, Location, Location
Achievements.Description: Secure every Tactical Location in Pacific City for the Agency, alone or with another Agent.

Achievements.Name: Pest Control
Achievements.Description: Clear out and close down a Freak Breach, alone or with another Agent.

Achievements.Name: The Closer
Achievements.Description: Close down every Freak Breach in Pacific City, alone or with another Agent.

Achievements.Name: Tower Power
Achievements.Description: Complete the final phase of Project Sunburst at Agency Tower, alone or with another Agent.

Achievements.Name: Tellin' Stories
Achievements.Description: Collect and listen to an Audio Log.

Achievements.Name: Closed Book
Achievements.Description: Collect and listen to every Audio Log in Pacific City.

Achievements.Name: In Plain Sight
Achievements.Description: Find and collect a Hidden Orb.

Achievements.Name: Sixth Sense
Achievements.Description: Find and collect every Hidden Orb in Pacific City.

Achievements.Name: First Rung of the Ladder
Achievements.Description: Find and collect an Agility Orb

Achievements.Name: King of the World
Achievements.Description: Find and collect every Agility Orb in Pacific City.

Achievements.Name: In the Net
Achievements.Description: Catch an Agility Renegade Orb or Driving Renegade Orb.

Achievements.Name: Renegade Runner
Achievements.Description: Find and collect every Renegade Agility Orb in Pacific City.

Achievements.Name: Renegade Racer
Achievements.Description: Find and collect every Renegade Driving Orb in Pacific City.

Achievements.Name: Speed Demon
Achievements.Description: Complete a Road or Rooftop Race

Achievements.Name: Street Racer
Achievements.Description: Complete every Road Race in Pacific City.

Achievements.Name: Rooftop Racer
Achievements.Description: Complete every Rooftop Race in Pacific City.

Achievements.Name: Wingsuit Racer
Achievements.Description: Glide through every Wingsuit Stunt Ring in Pacific City.

Achievements.Name: Stuntman
Achievements.Description: Jump a vehicle through every Vehicle Stunt Ring in Pacific City.

Achievements.Name: LIVE and let LIVE
Achievements.Description: Collect every Online Orb in Pacific City.

Achievements.Name: Who's the Daddy?
Achievements.Description: Develop each of your skills to their maximum levels.

Achievements.Name: Solid Block of Orbsome
Achievements.Description: Find and collect every Agility, Hidden, Renegade and Online Orb in Pacific City.

Achievements.Name: Jack of all Trades
Achievements.Description: Complete one of every objective type in Pacific City.

Achievements.Name: Pebble Dash
Achievements.Description: From the top of full-height Agency Tower, leap into the chimney stack and live to tell the tale.

Achievements.Name: City Glider
Achievements.Description: Wingsuit glide through the airspace of all islands in Pacific City without touching down.

Achievements.Name: Squad City Glider
Achievements.Description: 4 Agents, Wingsuit-glide through the airspace of all islands in city within 30 secs of leader.

Achievements.Name: Open up a Can
Achievements.Description: Kill 5 enemies with a single gas cylinder.

Achievements.Name: Co-op Keepy-Up
Achievements.Description: Pass a vehicle back and forth between Agents 3x using UV shotguns. Vehicle must not hit the ground.

Achievements.Name: Yippee-Kai-Yay
Achievements.Description: Drive an Agency SUV into an airborne helicopter.

Achievements.Name: Strike!
Achievements.Description: Kill 25 Freaks with thrown objects or vehicles.

Achievements.Name: Victory Roll
Achievements.Description: Alone or with another Agent, kill an enemy with a mounted turret while airborne and upside-down!

Achievements.Name: Mosh Pit
Achievements.Description: Land 20 successful hand-to-hand attacks in a chain. Under 3 secs between attacks to chain them.

Achievements.Name: Scarface
Achievements.Description: Use the minigun to amass 20 enemy kills in a 10 second period.

Achievements.Name: Zero Factor
Achievements.Description: Use a UV weapon to amass 20 Freak kills in a 10 second period.

Achievements.Name: Street Sweeper
Achievements.Description: While driving a vehicle kill 5 enemies in a single power slide.

Achievements.Name: Pin Cushion
Achievements.Description: Use Harpoon Gun to pin 5 enemies to a single vehicle.

Achievements.Name: Bomberman
Achievements.Description: Create 30 explosions in 60 seconds.

Achievements.Name: 25 Ways to Die
Achievements.Description: Find 25 unique ways to destroy your cloned body.

Achievements.Name: Car Jump
Achievements.Description: Leap from one fast moving vehicle to another.

Achievements.Name: Chopper Stomper
Achievements.Description: Leap from an airborne Agency helicopter and using a Ground Strike, kill at least one enemy.

Achievements.Name: Party Bus
Achievements.Description: Four Agents; one driver and three gunners, on a Battle Bus. Must jump through a Vehicle Stunt Ring.

Achievements.Name: Pile Driver
Achievements.Description: Kill 5 enemies with a single Ground Strike.
